    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
               
	<pb facs="liv_001935_0001" n="0001"/>

<opener>
<lb/><dateline rend="right"><placeName><geogName type="cataracts">Cataracts of <placeName><geogName type="river">Shire</geogName></placeName></geogName></placeName> 
<lb/><date when="1863-07-05">5<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> July 1863</date></dateline>
<lb/>    
<lb/><salute>My Dear Dr. Kirk</salute>
</opener>

<lb/><p>The new <persName><term type="occupation"><choice><sic>bishop</sic><corr>Bishop</corr></choice></term></persName>
<lb/>came up to us <date when="1863-07-04">yesterday</date>
<lb/>and recieved the
<lb/><bibl>Despatch</bibl> containing 
<lb/>our <choice><sic>recal</sic><corr>recall</corr></choice> the day
<lb/>before - The time
<lb/>appointed for us
<lb/>to be down at the
<lb/>mouth of the river<!-- geog: Mouth of Shire River -->
<lb/>is the end of this
<lb/>month and no
<lb/>salary is to be due </p>

<cb rend="vertical"/>
<ab>
<lb/>I recieved <bibl>2 <placeName><settlement type="village">Mazaro</settlement></placeName> notes</bibl> from
<lb/>you thanks - sorry you missed <persName>Orestes</persName>
</ab> 

	<pb facs="liv_001935_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/><p>after <date when="1863-12-31">31<hi rend="sup underline">st</hi> December</date>
<lb/>This has not been
<lb/>unlooked for by
<lb/>me - It rather relieves
<lb/>my mind about
<lb/>the Lady Nyassa
<lb/>as we can screw her
<lb/>together &amp; sell her in
<lb/><country>India</country><!-- Context is all. AW --> - As you
<lb/>know the <orgName>Portuguese</orgName> by
<lb/>clearing off the
<lb/>population finished
<lb/>our work but this
<lb/>is not adverted to
<lb/>in the <choice><sic>recal</sic><corr>recall</corr></choice> - perhaps
<lb/>it would have been
<lb/>impolitic - The difficulties

	<pb facs="liv_001935_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/>we encountered 
<lb/>adverted to - zeal &amp;
<lb/>perserverance &amp;c &amp;c
<lb/>praised but this
<lb/>"information we 
<lb/>have given is rather
<lb/>scant' say his
<lb/><persName>Lordship</persName><choice><sic>"</sic><corr/></choice> <space extent="1" unit="chars"/>Now
<lb/>you may go in
<lb/>on that to give
<lb/>a magnificant
<lb/><bibl>botanical work</bibl>
<lb/><bibl>economical</bibl> &amp;
<lb/>everything else at
<lb/><orgName>Government</orgName>
<lb/>expense - at least
<lb/>I mean to put that
<lb/>to him - </p>
<lb/><p>As we <choice><sic>cant</sic><corr>can't</corr></choice> come

	<pb facs="liv_001935_0004" n="0004"/>
<lb/>down with Pioneer
<lb/>though we could with
<lb/>Lady Nyassa I am
<lb/>going up to the <placeName><region>North
<lb/>end of <placeName><geogName type="lake">Lake Nyassa</geogName></placeName></region></placeName>
<lb/>directly to improve
<lb/>the intermediate time
<lb/>The <term type="tribe">Makololo</term>
<lb/>go with me - The boat was
<lb/>burned I think by
<lb/>accidental firing of
<lb/>the grass but by
<lb/>the <term type="tribe">Ajawa</term> say the
<lb/><term type="tribe">Maganja</term> - I <choice><sic>dont</sic><corr>don't</corr></choice>
<lb/>believe them as all
<lb/>the copper &amp; iron lay
<lb/>untouched below

	<pb facs="liv_001935_0005" n="0005"/>
<lb/><persName>J Reid</persName> is better - a
<lb/>smart dose of <term type="medicament">calomel</term>
<lb/>when <persName>Meller</persName> was down
<lb/>at the <orgName><placeName>Mission</placeName></orgName> cleared
<lb/>away spleen &amp; <w>every-
<lb break="no"/><supplied>-</supplied>thing</w> else - I persuaded
<lb/><persName>Meller</persName> to give the same
<lb/>to <persName>King</persName> and his 
<lb/><term type="ailment"><choice><orig>Haemorrhoids</orig><reg>Hemerroids</reg></choice></term> went
<lb/>apace - He was quite
<lb/><term type="ailment">bloodless</term> &amp; <term type="ailment">delirious</term>
<lb/>each night - but
<lb/>we took him up to 
<lb/><placeName><unclear>Mokurumadzi</unclear></placeName> &amp; he
<lb/>walked all the way home - - this is all
<lb/>by way of increasing

	<pb facs="liv_001935_0006" n="0006"/>
<lb/>your medical knowledge
<lb/><persName>Procter</persName> is ill &amp; retires
<lb/><persName>Rowley</persName> on his last
<lb/>legs <hi rend="underline">they say</hi>, too -
<lb/><persName>Waller</persName> ill yesterday
<lb/>the new <persName><term type="occupation"><choice><sic>bishop</sic><corr>Bishop</corr></choice></term></persName> a
<lb/>good cautious man
<lb/>thinks of trying the
<lb/>top of <placeName><geogName type="mountain">Merambala</geogName></placeName> -
<lb/>I am sure I welcome
<lb/>the new <orgName>squad</orgName> heartily
<lb/>though <persName>Rowley</persName> &amp;
<lb/>others would place
<lb/>all the blame of their
<lb/>fighting on me</p>

	<pb facs="liv_001935_0007" n="0007"/>
<lb/><p><term type="occupation">Teaching</term> is to be
<lb/>the order of the day
<lb/>He thinks it scandalous
<lb/>no effort has been
<lb/>made to convey
<lb/><term type="faith"><choice><sic>christian</sic><corr>Christian</corr></choice></term> knowledge
<lb/>He comes from the
<lb/><placeName><region><w><app><rdg>f</rdg><rdg>F</rdg></app>ens</w> of <placeName><region>Lincolnshire</region></placeName></region></placeName>
<lb/>and ought to be
<lb/>inured to <term type="ailment">malaria</term>
<lb/>I take the black
<lb/>whaler &amp; wish you
<lb/>were with me
<lb/>again - nearly
<lb/>all the <term type="tribe">Makololo</term>
<lb/>go but stop at
<lb/>some point to hunt
<lb/><term type="animal">elephants</term> while I go

	<pb facs="liv_001935_0008" n="0008"/>
<lb/>on with five in the boat</p>
<lb/><p>When <persName><choice><sic>Procters</sic><corr>Procter's</corr></choice></persName> hut was
<lb/>burned several guns going
<lb/>off made the <term type="tribe">Makololo</term>
<lb/>think the <orgName><placeName>mission</placeName></orgName> was
<lb/>attacked by an armed
<lb/>force - They at once
<lb/>rushed with spear &amp;c
<lb/>to the rescue - this is 
<lb/>per <persName>Blai<subst><del>r</del><add place="over-text">r</add></subst></persName> - if correct
<lb/>no fear need be <w>enter-
<lb break="no"/><supplied>-</supplied>tained</w> of them - attacking
<lb/>the <orgName><placeName>Mission</placeName></orgName> - My son
<lb/><persName>Robert</persName> is at <placeName><country>Natal</country></placeName>
<lb/>give him a kind word
<lb/>if you see him and
<lb/>may God Bless you</p>

<closer>
<lb/><salute>Yours with Affection</salute><!-- Change as appropriate -->
<lb/><signed><persName>David Livingstone</persName></signed><!-- Change as appropriate --> 
</closer>


            </div>
        </body>
